description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 2 of 4 of the live November match up between Team Ice and The Goddesses.
Round 2 starts off as rough and tumble as the first; all four girls are fighting for honor and respect in front of the live audience. No one wants to get fingered, no one wants to submit to a brutal crushing hold. All four girls are giving 100% and the action is getting brutal.
Which team wants it more, and who will take the lead going into the final round?
title: Brutal non-scripted Tag Team Action
